House set to vote this week on gun reform bills
05:25
copied!
The House will vote on two gun control measures this week. While they should pass the House, their fate in the Senate is up for debate. With Capitol Hill jammed, big business is stepping up. Stephanie Ruhle is joined by Dick’s Sporting Goods’ CEO, Ed Stacks, to discuss his choice to change the way his company approached gun reform after the Parkland shooting.Feb. 26, 2019
